# Design System Documentation

## Overview

This document outlines the design system for our document-based CRM application. The application uses a clean, minimal aesthetic inspired by modern note-taking apps like Apple Notes, with additional structure to support CRM functionality.

## Design Philosophy

The design emphasizes:
- **Simplicity**: Clean, distraction-free interface that puts content first
- **Focus**: Minimal UI elements that disappear when not needed
- **Hierarchy**: Clear visual hierarchy to distinguish between different types of information
- **Accessibility**: High contrast text and properly sized interactive elements

## Technology Stack

The application's design system is built using:
- **Tailwind CSS**: For utility-based styling
- **shadcn/ui**: Component library built on Radix UI primitives
- **Radix UI**: For accessible, unstyled components
- **Lucide React**: For consistent iconography

## Color Palette

The application uses a professional, minimalist color palette:

- **Primary**: `hsl(222.2 47.4% 11.2%)` - A dark slate/black color used for primary buttons and actions
- **Primary Foreground**: White text on primary backgrounds
- **Neutral Gray Scale**:
  - Background: `#FFFFFF` (white)
  - Subtle backgrounds: `#F9FAFB` (gray-50)
  - Borders: `#E5E7EB` (gray-200)
  - Muted text: `#6B7280` (gray-500)
  - Primary text: `#111827` (gray-900)
- **Accent/Functional Colors**:
  - Destructive: `#EF4444` (red-600) - Used for delete actions and warnings
  - Blue Accent: `#3B82F6` (blue-600) - Used for Magic AI functionality

The theme is configured using the "professional" variant in theme.json with a border radius of 0.5 units.

## Typography

The application uses a system-first approach to typography:

- **Font Family**: System UI fonts (San Francisco on macOS/iOS, Segoe UI on Windows, etc.)
- **Base Font Size**: 16px (1rem)
- **Font Weights**:
  - Regular: 400
  - Medium: 500
  - Semibold: 600
  - Bold: 700
- **Line Height**: 1.5 for body text, 1.2 for headings

### Type Scale

- **Heading 1**: 2rem (32px), Semibold
- **Heading 2**: 1.5rem (24px), Semibold
- **Heading 3**: 1.25rem (20px), Semibold
- **Heading 4**: 1.125rem (18px), Semibold
- **Body**: 1rem (16px), Regular
- **Small/Caption**: 0.875rem (14px), Regular

## Component Library

The application uses shadcn/ui components with customizations to match our design language:

### Button Variants

- **Default**: Black background with white text
- **Destructive**: Red background (`#EF4444`) with white text
- **Outline**: Transparent with border, changes on hover
- **Secondary**: Light gray background with dark text
- **Ghost**: Transparent background that shows background on hover
- **Link**: Underlined text with no background

### Button Sizes

- **Default**: Height of 40px (h-10) with horizontal padding of 16px (px-4)
- **Small**: Height of 36px (h-9) with horizontal padding of 12px (px-3)
- **Large**: Height of 44px (h-11) with horizontal padding of 32px (px-8)
- **Icon**: Square button with size of 40px (h-10 w-10)

### Application-Specific Components

- **Note Editor**:
  - Clean, white background
  - Rich text capabilities using TipTap editor
  - Special styling for task items and @mentions
  - Proper typography using Tailwind's prose utilities

- **Toolbar**:
  - Light border at the bottom
  - Icon-based Toggle components with tooltips
  - Compact layout (h-8 w-8 for buttons) to maximize content area

- **Sidebar**:
  - List of notes with title and truncated preview
  - Active item highlighting
  - Collapsible for more editing space

- **Magic AI Button**:
  - Wand icon (`Wand2` from Lucide React)
  - Pulse animation during processing (animate-pulse)
  - Blue accent color (`text-blue-500`) to highlight AI functionality

- **Dialog Components**:
  - Alert dialogs for confirmations
  - Modals for more complex interactions
  - Clean, white backgrounds with proper spacing

## Icons

The application uses Lucide React icons throughout the interface for consistency. Icons are typically:

- Size: 16px (h-4 w-4) in the toolbar, slightly larger elsewhere
- Consistent scale and alignment
- Used with proper accessibility attributes

## Spacing System

The spacing system follows Tailwind's default spacing scale, which is built on a 0.25rem (4px) base unit:

- **0.25rem (p-1)**: Minimum spacing, tight connections
- **0.5rem (p-2)**: Default spacing between related items
- **1rem (p-4)**: Standard component padding
- **1.5rem (p-6)**: Separation between distinct sections
- **2rem (p-8)**: Major section breaks

## Animation

Animations are subtle and functional:

- Transition durations: 150-200ms with ease-in-out timing
- Loading indicators: 
  - Spinning border animation for general loading
  - Pulse animation (`animate-pulse`) for Magic AI processing

## Responsive Design

The application follows Tailwind's responsive breakpoints:
- **sm**: 640px
- **md**: 768px
- **lg**: 1024px
- **xl**: 1280px
- **2xl**: 1536px

The interface is optimized for desktop-first with adaptations for smaller screens.

## Accessibility

The design system prioritizes accessibility through:

- High contrast between text and backgrounds
- Keyboard navigation support via Radix UI primitives
- Proper focus states with visible outlines
- Semantic HTML and ARIA attributes
- Tooltips for icon-only buttons

## Future Considerations

- Dark mode support
- Additional theme customization options
- Enhanced visualizations for sales pipeline
- Mobile-specific optimizations
